posting_body: ['The Retreat at Fox Hollow Apartments boasts beautiful lush landscapes that offer unencumbered views of stunning natural surroundings.', 'Wake up to breathtaking views of the nearby mountains and enjoy an eclectic neighborhood with a dynamic feel.', 'Calling the Retreat at Fox Hollow “home” is easy when you step into your luxurious apartment, complete with a private balcony, fireplace, alarm system, and even your in-home washer and dryer.', 'Life can be truly comfortable when you consider the vast array of amenities that will be right at your fingertips at The Retreat at Fox Hollow.', '-Accepts Credit Card Payments', '-Individual Alarm Systems', '-Public Transportation', '-24-Hour Fitness Studio with Virtual Trainer', '-Direct Ground Floor Entry', '-Gas Log Fireplaces', '-Cable Ready', '-Ceiling fans', '-Rocky Mountain Views', '-Outdoor Firepit and Barbecue Grills', '-Direct Access One and Two Car Garages', '-Air Conditioning', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Our pricing changes daily.', 'Please call or email us today for updated pricing and availability.']
